---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="The story behind Battle Beast playing cards.">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="section-title">Our Story</h1>

      <div class="prose">
        <p class="lead">
          Battle Beast is built by three friends who are passionate about playing cards and the joy of games.
        </p>

        <p>
          We're a fairly young team — but our love for card games runs deep. From late-night sessions to heated tournament runs, games have always been at the center of our friendships. Battle Beast is our way of putting that energy into something others can play too.
        </p>

        <p>
          We wanted a game that felt exciting, fast, and full of surprises. One where the creature on your card felt alive and ready for action. So we made it ourselves.
        </p>

        <p>
          We're an independent studio. Every sale goes directly into printing the next expansion and keeping the lights on. We appreciate every player who takes a chance on us.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="values">
        <div class="value">
          <h3>Independent</h3>
          <p>No corporate backing. No algorithmic card drops. Just us, the artists, and you.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value">
          <h3>Fair</h3>
          <p>Every card is available without loot boxes. Buy a deck, know what you're getting.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value">
          <h3>Competitive</h3>
          <p>Designed from day one for tournament play. Skill wins, not wallet size.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <a href="/buy" class="btn btn-primary">Join the Fight</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .prose p {
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.35rem !important;
    color: var(--color-text) !important;
    font-style: italic;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-primary);
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem !important;
  }

  .values {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .value {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid #1f1f1f;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: #111;
  }

  .value h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .value p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--color-muted); }
</style>
